strategies: I have been to many of the places named. I would think something like Pasadena; parade; great museum; Pasadena.
familiar: Have I been there? Often; yes. If not; have I ever heard of it? Often yes; in a meeting.
memorable: Many names like that are memorable to me. But the more vowels in the name; the more difficult for me.
unique: If I've only heard of one of them; then I deemed the unique.
realistic: As I said; a town can be named pretty much anything. So most names are realistic.
